Full disclosure: I used to hate my legs. Thought that Id never see muscle definition. Thought that Id always have chunky thunder thighs. But last night while I was BBQing, and unpacking more of my new apartment, I caught a glimpse of myself in the mirror and actually did a double take??. Im currently recovering from my 3rd surgery in 3 years, but all the hard work Ive put in over the last three years since I started my fitness journey haS paid off! ?
.
.
The problem with that statement I said earlier in the quotes and the way I used to think, see and feel about myself was 100% - - ME. .
.
.
We are in control of our bodies. We are in control of what we put into our bodies. We are in control of how we move our bodies. We are in control of believing whether or not we can accomplish something. We are in control of whether or not we believe in ourselves. We are in control of pushing ourselves and challenging ourselves to accomplish things that perhaps scare the shit out of us and goals that may slightly seem far fetched or out of reach. But let me tell you something though, they are only slightly out of reach if you BELIEVE that they are. REACH a little further for them and dont stop until youre satisfied with your accomplishments no matter how long it takes!! Never change the goal, but be flexible with the timeframe it might take to accomplish what you want.????
.
.
.
As soon as Im able to workout again - look out!! Im giving myself a epic transformation for Christmas and Im READY to be OBSESSED!! Are you finally ready to get started with me and get into amazing shape from home? My next Bootcamp starts on June 18th. Youll get all the tools you need - you just need to show up with me everyday and use them ?. 30 min a day is all it takes. 
If I can do it, so can you. 
Shaunna.dunmore@gmail.com
